data.description: 4 bedroom 4 bath home on one acre of beautiful level property. 2 master bedrooms with access to the balcony.  Walkout basement with plenty of storage. Includes 1800 sq ft building with an apartment and two kitchens, Additional living quarters for quests or possible rental income. 16X30 unfinished carport attached to apartment building that could be used for storage. Only a few miles from the WindRock Campground and Bike Park.  This is part of an estate, Seller is planning an estate sale and has many items left to move out of the dwellings. Professional Photos coming soon. Seller has made many upgrades and is selling AS-IS.
